1
00:00:58,800 --> 00:00:59,680
What do you want?

2
00:01:00,360 --> 00:01:01,400
Cut the crap.

3
00:01:01,760 --> 00:01:02,920
No vendors allowed here.

4
00:01:02,920 --> 00:01:04,040
Says who? Get lost.

5
00:01:05,160 --> 00:01:06,440
What you're doing is illegal.

6
00:01:07,280 --> 00:01:08,120
What are you doing?

7
00:01:09,080 --> 00:01:10,160
What am I doing?

8
00:01:11,160 --> 00:01:12,320
Go ask around.

9
00:01:12,560 --> 00:01:13,480
Find out who I am.

10
00:01:13,680 --> 00:01:14,960
Who let you set up shop here?

11
00:01:15,520 --> 00:01:17,040
Did I give you permission?

12
00:01:18,040 --> 00:01:19,240
Old bastard.

13
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:20,400
You got a death wish?

14
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:21,800
Qin Jianping.

15
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:23,280
Don't drag this out.

16
00:01:23,440 --> 00:01:24,480
Enough already.

17
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:26,000
The old guy just got here.

18
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:26,960
He only handed out a few flyers.

19
00:01:26,960 --> 00:01:27,960
And he still has to pay you?

20
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:30,640
You little punk.

21
00:01:30,760 --> 00:01:32,040
Mind your own damn business.

22
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:37,320
Beat him up.

23
00:01:39,040 --> 00:01:39,880
Beat him to death!

24
00:01:40,640 --> 00:01:41,920
That'll teach you to butt in.

25
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:44,520
Stop fighting! Stop it!

26
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:46,920
Brother.

27
00:01:47,720 --> 00:01:48,600
Stop hitting him!

28
00:01:49,600 --> 00:01:50,160
Get lost!

29
00:01:50,160 --> 00:01:51,360
Stop it, now!

30
00:01:51,360 --> 00:01:51,920
Scram!

31
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:55,720
You little punk.

32
00:01:57,120 --> 00:01:58,040
Boss, boss.

33
00:02:01,440 --> 00:02:01,960
Lin You.

34
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:09,360
Everyone back off.

35
00:02:10,039 --> 00:02:10,680
Speak.

36
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,080
What the hell do you want?

37
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:15,800
Give me a piece of turf.

38
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:17,280
And some cash.

39
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:18,240
Let me work for you.

40
00:02:18,640 --> 00:02:19,440
What's that supposed to mean?

41
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:21,440
Since I'm not getting anything,

42
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:23,800
and my brother will suffer when he's out,

43
00:02:23,920 --> 00:02:25,720
I might as well avenge him first.

44
00:02:25,720 --> 00:02:26,240
Tell you what,

45
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:28,040
if you walk out of here alive today,

46
00:02:28,040 --> 00:02:29,080
I'll agree to your terms.

47
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:38,880
Help!

48
00:02:39,480 --> 00:02:40,280
Help!

49
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:41,200
Mister!

50
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,760
My brother helped you before.

51
00:02:42,760 --> 00:02:43,920
Please let me hide inside!

52
00:02:44,480 --> 00:02:45,200
Mister!

53
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:46,600
Mister!

54
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:48,040
Mister!

55
00:02:48,040 --> 00:02:49,280
I know you're in there!

56
00:02:49,440 --> 00:02:50,840
Open the door, mister! Run!

57
00:02:50,920 --> 00:02:52,080
Let me hide in there! Run!

58
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:53,200
You sure can run, can't you?

59
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:54,080
Run, mister!

60
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:55,560
I know you're in there!

61
00:02:55,600 --> 00:02:56,000
Where do you think you're going?

62
00:02:56,200 --> 00:02:57,400
Stay back, you punks!

63
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:58,800
Stay back! Run!

64
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:00,960
Trying to steal our turf?

65
00:03:01,480 --> 00:03:02,280
Mister!

66
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:03,600
Don't move, old man.

67
00:03:04,160 --> 00:03:05,640
Mister!

68
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:10,560
Mister!

69
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:26,560
Don't think a crappy piece of land

70
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:27,800
makes you the boss.

71
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:29,600
Help!

72
00:03:29,600 --> 00:03:30,520
You ain't shit.

73
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:54,320
Boss Wang

74
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:56,040
We meet again.

75
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:58,320
How have you been?

76
00:03:59,160 --> 00:04:00,520
They didn't rough you up, did they?

77
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:05,640
You've drawn so many talismans in your life,

78
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:08,600
yet you never drew one to save your own skin.

79
00:04:08,880 --> 00:04:09,680
Kid,

80
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:12,640
I was wrong back then.

81
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:14,160
I apologize.

82
00:04:15,480 --> 00:04:16,760
It's all my fault.

83
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:21,480
I won't try to make excuses.

84
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:23,480
Punish me however you want.

85
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,400
But Liu Liu and Lin You

86
00:04:25,400 --> 00:04:27,040
have nothing to do with this.

87
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:28,000
I'm begging you,

88
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:29,800
don't drag them into this.

89
00:04:30,760 --> 00:04:31,960
No need to apologize to me.

90
00:04:32,960 --> 00:04:34,760
Since Lin You sees you as family,

91
00:04:35,160 --> 00:04:36,960
I naturally won't mistreat you.

92
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:45,520
Lin You.

93
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:50,200
Do you know why I wouldn't let you follow him?

94
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:54,080
Because of him,

95
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:57,240
you spent ten whole years in prison.

96
00:04:58,840 --> 00:05:00,680
He ignored me back then,

97
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:01,720
and now, for his godson,

98
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:03,160
he kicks you aside again.

99
00:05:03,400 --> 00:05:04,840
Good deeds don't always go rewarded.

100
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:07,360
Even if you once saved him,

101
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:08,360
when danger comes,

102
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:10,080
he'll still kick you to the curb.

103
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,520
Only true family

104
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:17,840
will always have your back.

105
00:05:21,320 --> 00:05:23,040
Why didn't you tell me this sooner?

106
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:27,360
Some things, if you don't hear them yourself,

107
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:28,920
you wouldn't believe me.

108
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:32,120
In this world,

109
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:34,840
kindness isn't a good thing.

110
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:36,840
You must remember those

111
00:05:36,840 --> 00:05:38,400
who have hurt you,

112
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:40,200
then grow stronger quickly,

113
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:42,000
and crush them beneath your feet.

114
00:05:47,200 --> 00:05:48,520
Why is she here?

115
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:54,040
A partner.

116
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:05,120
What the hell do you want?

117
00:06:07,640 --> 00:06:08,280
Me?

118
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:13,240
Just helping out.

119
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:23,200
Just spit it out already.

120
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:29,160
No need to rush.

121
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:35,880
I could easily take Wang Shengjin out myself,

122
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:38,520
but Lin You would hate me.

123
00:06:41,320 --> 00:06:43,840
You know that old fraud is lying to you.

124
00:06:44,960 --> 00:06:47,720
If you expose him for me,

125
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:50,200
and help Lin You see his true colors,

126
00:06:51,320 --> 00:06:53,520
that would change everything.

127
00:06:54,440 --> 00:06:56,640
In return, I'll perform a ritual for you

128
00:06:56,960 --> 00:06:58,520
to finish what you left undone.

129
00:06:58,840 --> 00:06:59,680
So?

130
00:06:59,840 --> 00:07:01,360
So we should work together.

131
00:07:04,960 --> 00:07:06,800
I really like your personality.

132
00:07:07,640 --> 00:07:09,520
You're someone capable of great things.

133
00:07:10,960 --> 00:07:11,920
Helping you

134
00:07:12,880 --> 00:07:14,360
is also helping myself.

135
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:18,200
In a way,

136
00:07:19,960 --> 00:07:21,400
I'm also helping Lin You.

137
00:07:43,080 --> 00:07:43,960
Let's work together.

138
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:49,880
I'll help you get revenge,

139
00:07:51,520 --> 00:07:52,920
and you help me get mine.

140
00:07:54,440 --> 00:07:56,480
Let's commit to doing one thing together,

141
00:07:58,080 --> 00:07:59,880
something we do for ourselves.

142
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,760
Where have you been all this time?

143
00:08:41,679 --> 00:08:43,280
It's almost over, Lin You.

144
00:08:45,040 --> 00:08:46,040
Once your brother

145
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:48,720
finishes this ritual for me,

146
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:54,880
Yaoyao will finally be free.

147
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:04,400
When does the ritual start?

148
00:09:05,760 --> 00:09:06,680
In a week.

149
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:10,240
I even had a master pick an auspicious date.

150
00:09:10,920 --> 00:09:12,400
I don't really believe in this stuff,

151
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:14,680
but for your friend's sake,

152
00:09:15,560 --> 00:09:16,560
I'm willing to do it.

153
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:43,560
A person's fate

154
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:46,960
is determined by every small thought

155
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:48,160
they have.

156
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:51,800
Since you made that choice back then,

157
00:09:52,680 --> 00:09:54,440
now you have to face the consequences.

158
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:00,520
That's just how life works.

159
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:02,280
If you make a mistake, own up to it.

160
00:10:03,680 --> 00:10:04,840
Take your beating standing tall.

161
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:07,680
Some things

162
00:10:10,040 --> 00:10:11,280
just have to be done.

163
00:10:20,640 --> 00:10:21,680
Daji, I'll go tear it down.

164
00:10:26,520 --> 00:10:27,320
Okay.

165
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:34,520
Brother You,

166
00:10:34,760 --> 00:10:35,720
everyone's here.

167
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:37,160
We'll get started once you come out.

168
00:11:15,040 --> 00:11:16,720
Come on, guys, get ready.

169
00:11:17,040 --> 00:11:18,400
The sooner we start, the sooner we finish.

170
00:11:18,400 --> 00:11:19,080
Wait.

171
00:11:21,920 --> 00:11:22,880
The owner isn't here.

172
00:11:23,160 --> 00:11:24,800
What gives you the right to tear down their house?

173
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:26,280
Ma'am,

174
00:11:26,400 --> 00:11:27,880
we have a sales contract.

175
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:28,760
Boss Wang already signed it.

176
00:11:28,760 --> 00:11:29,520
Bullshit!

177
00:11:30,160 --> 00:11:31,480
He never mentioned it to me.

178
00:11:31,960 --> 00:11:32,760
Where's the contract?

179
00:11:33,280 --> 00:11:34,280
Show it to me.

180
00:11:34,560 --> 00:11:36,320
Who carries a contract around with them?

181
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:37,520
Keep this up and I'll call the cops.

182
00:11:37,520 --> 00:11:38,280
Go ahead, call them!

183
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:40,040
We'll see about that.

184
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:42,000
If I don't see Wang Shengjin today,

185
00:11:42,520 --> 00:11:44,080
none of you are touching this house.

186
00:11:44,720 --> 00:11:46,760
So talking nicely doesn't work, huh?

187
00:11:46,760 --> 00:11:47,560
What? What are you gonna do?

188
00:11:47,560 --> 00:11:48,600
You wanna lay hands on me?

189
00:11:48,600 --> 00:11:49,920
Everything he said is true.

190
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:04,400
I'm sorry.

191
00:12:15,960 --> 00:12:16,440
Sis.

192
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:24,120
Where the hell have you been?

193
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:28,280
Why didn't you answer your phone?

194
00:12:29,720 --> 00:12:30,680
And you never came home.

195
00:12:32,520 --> 00:12:34,680
Do you know how many nights I looked for you?

196
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:37,160
I had to take care of Zhou Yi at the hospital.

197
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:39,200
And Old Wang disappeared too.

198
00:12:40,080 --> 00:12:41,360
If I hadn't come here today,

199
00:12:42,160 --> 00:12:43,400
the house would be gone.

200
00:12:44,680 --> 00:12:46,800
What the hell are you all trying to do?

201
00:12:49,160 --> 00:12:50,040
Just go home first.

202
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:52,120
I'll explain later.

203
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:53,200
I'm not going anywhere.

204
00:12:53,360 --> 00:12:54,520
You're staying right here today

205
00:12:54,520 --> 00:12:55,560
and explaining yourself.

206
00:12:59,520 --> 00:13:01,360
Did these people lead you astray?

207
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:03,440
Tell me the truth.

208
00:13:03,480 --> 00:13:04,320
What are you trying to do?

209
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:05,680
Are you really tearing down our home?

210
00:13:11,280 --> 00:13:12,880
Old Wang signed the contract.

211
00:13:14,520 --> 00:13:16,000
This stopped being home a long time ago.

212
00:13:20,120 --> 00:13:21,400
Drive my sister home.

213
00:13:23,160 --> 00:13:23,920
Don't touch me!

214
00:13:23,920 --> 00:13:24,640
Get your hands off me!

215
00:13:24,640 --> 00:13:25,280
I'm telling you,

216
00:13:25,280 --> 00:13:26,400
you're going to explain this to me today.

217
00:13:26,400 --> 00:13:27,720
Stop making a scene, sis.

218
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:33,080
Why are you here?

219
00:13:36,200 --> 00:13:37,000
Nothing.

220
00:13:37,680 --> 00:13:38,680
Just getting some air.

221
00:13:50,160 --> 00:13:50,960
You're awake.

222
00:13:53,280 --> 00:13:54,480
If I hadn't woken up,

223
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:55,960
we wouldn't have a home left.

224
00:13:58,400 --> 00:13:59,240
What do you have to say?

225
00:14:00,240 --> 00:14:01,600
I have to tear this place down.

226
00:14:07,960 --> 00:14:09,160
Unbelievable.

227
00:14:09,400 --> 00:14:10,200
Lin You,

228
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:12,720
do you really have to be this ruthless?

229
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:15,400
Since none of them want it,

230
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:17,240
why keep it around?

231
00:14:19,040 --> 00:14:19,840
Fine.

232
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:22,880
Looks like you've made up your mind.

233
00:14:23,640 --> 00:14:24,440
Of course.

234
00:14:26,040 --> 00:14:27,200
A worthless loser like you,

235
00:14:27,720 --> 00:14:28,560
how can you possibly stop me?

236
00:14:28,560 --> 00:14:30,320
Lin You, how can you say that?

237
00:14:36,440 --> 00:14:37,080
Sis.

238
00:14:38,160 --> 00:14:39,080
He's right.

239
00:14:40,840 --> 00:14:42,480
There's nothing we can do here.

240
00:14:45,880 --> 00:14:47,280
What's there to say

241
00:14:48,520 --> 00:14:49,960
to a criminal?

242
00:14:53,840 --> 00:14:54,520
Let's go, sis.

243
00:15:12,440 --> 00:15:13,320
Come on, boys.

244
00:15:13,440 --> 00:15:14,800
Let's get to work, get to work!
